# This project uses the packages in [package.json](mdc:package.json) for the following:

- Next.js (Pages Router) v15.2.1 - React framework for production
- TypeScript v5.8.2 - Static type checking
- React v19.0.0 - UI library
- Radix UI - Headless component primitives:
  - Accordion, Alert Dialog, Avatar
  - Dialog, Dropdown Menu, Navigation
  - Forms (Checkbox, Radio, Select)
  - And many more UI components
- Styling & UI:
  - Tailwind CSS v4.0.10 - Utility-first CSS
  - tailwindcss-animate - Animation utilities
  - class-variance-authority - Component variants
  - clsx & tailwind-merge - Class name utilities
  - lucide-react - Icon library
  - next-themes - Theme management

- Form Management:
  - react-hook-form - Form state management
  - zod - Schema validation
  - @hookform/resolvers - Form validation integration

- Data Visualization:
  - recharts - Charting library
  - @react-pdf/renderer - PDF generation

- Date Handling:
  - date-fns - Date manipulation
  - react-day-picker - Date picker component

- Additional UI Features:
  - sonner - Toast notifications
  - vaul - Drawer component
  - embla-carousel-react - Carousel component
  - react-resizable-panels - Resizable layout panels